Merchant Location:
Why Advertise Financing?
Give your sales a boost when you advertise financing.
PayPal helps turn browsers into buyers with financing from PayPal Credit®. Your customers have more time to pay, while you get paid up front – at no additional cost to you. Use PayPal’s free banner ads that let you advertise PayPal Credit® financing as a payment option when your customers check out with PayPal. The PayPal Advertising Program has been shown to generate additional purchases as well as increase consumer's average purchase sizes by 15% or more. See Details.
Prodajno mesto:
Zakaj oglaševati financiranje?
Povečajte vašo prodajo, ko oglašujete financiranje.
PayPal vam pomaga konvertirati brskalnike v kupce s pomočjo financiranja iz PayPal Credit®. Vaše stranje imajo več časa za plačilo, medtem ko vi dobite plačilo vnaprej – brez dodatnih stroškov za vas. Uporabite brezplačne oglaševalske pasice PayPal, ki vam omogočajo oglaševati financiranje PayPal Credit® kot možnost plačila, ko vaše stranke plačajo s PayPal. Izkazalo se je, da PayPal Advertising Program generira dodatne nakupe kot tudi poveča povprečni nakup potrošnikov do 15% ali več. Poglejte podrobnosti.
